# Admin-uploaded images land here via /api/images/upload.
#
# Path convention: assets/images/uploads/{yyyy}-{mm}/{slug}-{short-hash}.{ext}
# so a year's worth of uploads stays browsable in the GitHub tree without
# scrolling forever.
#
# Files in this folder are committed as part of admin PRs along with the
# content edit that references them. They are not deleted automatically
# when an override stops referencing them.
